.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
House: futuristic, cottage, wooden, palace, ranch-style, art-deco, tower
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, british, chinese, dutch, egyptian, french, german
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, swisher, havana, vegafina, montecristo, pall-mall, baccarat
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: july, may, april, december, september, october, february
 1. the vegafina-smoker is on the far right##1
 2. the montecristo-smoker is the dutch##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in september is the havana-smoker##1
 4. the british is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 5. the australian is on the right of the german##1
 6. the cottage house is the havana-smoker##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the egyptian##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's birthday is in february and the french##2
 9. the egyptian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
10. the wooden house is in the middle##1
11. the oliveros-smoker is the ranch-style house##1
12. the ranch-style house is the person who's birthday is in july##1
13. the futuristic house is on the left of the chinese##1
14. the french is the person who's birthday is in april##1
15. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the german##1
16. the cottage house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
17. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the chinese##1
18. the tower house is on the right of the egyptian##1
19. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
